item.description: ocis-php-sdk This SDK allows you to interact with ownCloud Infinite Scale (oCIS) storage using PHP. Documentation You can find a rendered version of the API documentation in our dev docs. To render the documentation locally, use the phpDocumentor to run it in the local repo. E.g.: docker run --rm -v ${PWD}:/data phpdoc/phpdoc:3 After that you will find the documentation inside the docs folder. :exclamation: This SDK is still under heavy development and is not yet ready for production use, the API might change!
